      <title>北方信托下调欧洲股票投资评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/northern-trust-downgrades-european-equity-exposure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northern Trust Asset Management 首席投资官 Anwiti Bahuguna 表示，该公司已下调了对欧洲股票的资产配置权重。她在彭博电视台表示：“我们刚刚对该地区持中立态度。目前情况还不足以让我们减持。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/northern-trust-downgrades-european-equity-exposure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:08:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行再次降息，为半点利率调整打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/riksbank-cuts-rate-a-quarter-point-and-opens-door-to-bigger-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行将借贷成本下调四分之一个百分点，并表示未来几个月可能采取更大举措，以刺激低迷的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/riksbank-cuts-rate-a-quarter-point-and-opens-door-to-bigger-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利联合信贷银行收购 CNP 和安联意大利人寿保险公司股份，首席执行官关注薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-buys-cnp-allianz-italy-life-stakes-as-ceo-eyes-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于首席执行官 Andrea Orcel 着眼于更高的费用和盈利能力，UniCredit SpA 正将其与 CNP Assurances 和 Allianz 共同运营的意大利人寿保险业务收归公司内部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-buys-cnp-allianz-italy-life-stakes-as-ceo-eyes-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行的奥塞尔表示，他不会竞选德国商业银行董事会席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-s-orcel-says-he-won-t-ask-for-commerzbank-board-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[UniCredit SpA 首席执行官 Andrea Orcel 表示，他不会为其贷方德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 寻求监事会席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-s-orcel-says-he-won-t-ask-for-commerzbank-board-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村因操纵日本债券市场面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司因涉嫌操纵日本政府债券期货市场而面临 2180 万日元（152,000 美元）的罚款，这对日本最大的经纪公司来说是一个在证券交易复苏期间的挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行利率悬念将成为托马斯·乔丹的告别</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/snb-rate-cliffhanger-will-be-jordan-s-farewell-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托马斯·乔丹作为瑞士央行行长所做出的最终利率决定充满悬念，可能令投资者感到意外——就像他任职期间的其他关键时刻一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/snb-rate-cliffhanger-will-be-jordan-s-farewell-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着怀疑情绪的出现，中国股市涨势失去动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市周三收盘走高，但由于人们担心周二宣布的一系列支持措施是否会扭转经济形势，涨幅较早前有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/chinese-stocks-extend-gains-on-continued-stimulus-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
